            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "《美人魚》︱「鄭總」真身涉猥褻兒童被刑拘  曾投資周星馳作品換演出",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"《美人魚》中的「鄭總」涉嫌在海南猥褻多名兒童遭刑事拘留。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/8705e45156b886cf86afafe3a78b1bb2/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250219/_2025021922170589505.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">《美人魚》中的「鄭總」涉嫌在海南猥褻多名兒童遭刑事拘留。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>娛樂圈名人、曾參演電影「鄭總」一角廣為人知的鄭某某，1月因涉嫌猥褻兒童被海南海口公安刑事拘留。公開資料顯示，「鄭總」為周星馳作品《美人魚》一角，演出者為鄭冀峰，據指他有份投資《美人魚》，要求演出一個角色。澎湃新聞19日晚獲海口公安局證實，鄭冀峰因涉嫌猥褻兒童被刑拘，已報檢察院對其批准逮捕。\n\n</p><h2>傳藉選童星趁機猥褻</h2>\n<p>法律自媒體「法度law」日前獨家報道，指曾參演過香港某知名演員導演的電影中「鄭總」一角的鄭某某傳因涉嫌猥褻兒童，於今年1月被海口市公安局龍華分局刑事拘留。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"「鄭總」被指涉嫌猥褻兒童被海口公安刑拘。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e2fdcb43c62bc96b14fe5b5aa0729bb5/2025-02/173996837335597.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        「鄭總」被指涉嫌猥褻兒童被海口公安刑拘。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"鄭冀峰在周星馳作品《美人魚》中有扮投資及演出。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/57ac3253ae23b7d2d5bfb4b7fb5ca05b/2025-02/v2-da36134f005808211f4e8e686cd0a3c7_1440w.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄭冀峰在周星馳作品《美人魚》中有扮投資及演出。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"鄭冀峰在《美人魚》中扮演「鄭總」獲網民大讚。《美人魚》截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4989847fd8ed4eccea9ed8b2017f8352/2025-02/4d3fd4fcedbb40689123f32b93bdd985.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄭冀峰在《美人魚》中扮演「鄭總」獲網民大讚。《美人魚》截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"鄭冀峰在《美人魚》中扮演「鄭總」獲網民大讚。《美人魚》截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cb9e9f42d4ce70f93685c8361dbb7640/2025-02/130b57d3c4e24bba8f3de49bc4e6195a.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄭冀峰在《美人魚》中扮演「鄭總」獲網民大讚。《美人魚》截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"鄭冀峰在《美人魚》中扮演「鄭總」獲網民大讚。《美人魚》截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e7a09b29bdc27176f0f9c09a1a9a51e8/2025-02/4545653.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄭冀峰在《美人魚》中扮演「鄭總」獲網民大讚。《美人魚》截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"鄭冀峰在《美人魚》中扮演「鄭總」獲網民大讚。《美人魚》截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fd4c6f0910d74efb8ef2b0474d7ce44e/2025-02/12123233.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄭冀峰在《美人魚》中扮演「鄭總」獲網民大讚。《美人魚》截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"鄭冀峰(右)在周星馳作品《美人魚》中有扮投資及演出。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/45423cb5925e4db3511f93478f20c43e/2025-02/d6f14771b7834e87a2569e217dd9760e.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄭冀峰(右)在周星馳作品《美人魚》中有扮投資及演出。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"鄭冀峰在《美人魚》中扮演「鄭總」獲網民大讚。《美人魚》劇照\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/aa58109d31355e016c0538c814766869/2025-02/INjUVYvkJFdN7oXb23JE0w-pM8_3XesA3P_rTdz_600.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄭冀峰在《美人魚》中扮演「鄭總」獲網民大讚。《美人魚》劇照\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"鄭冀峰在《美人魚》中有扮投資及演出。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/23572a556318b18eb3fe0b8f560fa567/2025-02/mp59415804_1455774000524_2_th.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄭冀峰在《美人魚》中有扮投資及演出。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"知情者指鄭冀峰正被羈押在海口市第一看守所。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ebc647ad8e82ef3a81cdefa80ae2ce49/2025-02/_1_____45.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        知情者指鄭冀峰正被羈押在海口市第一看守所。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞 :<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/china-taiwan/3407163/%E5%8F%B0%E8%97%9D%E4%BA%BA%E9%BB%83%E5%AD%90%E4%BD%BC%E5%81%B7%E6%8B%8D%E8%AB%96%E5%A3%87%E8%B3%BC%E6%9C%AA%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E4%B8%8D%E9%9B%85%E7%89%87-%E5%88%A4%E5%88%918%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E4%BD%B5%E7%A7%91%E7%BD%B0%E9%87%9110%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83\">台藝人黃子佼偷拍論壇購未成年少女不雅片 判刑8個月 併科罰金10萬元</a>\n</p>\n<p>當時，辦案機關未有證實上述報道。至18日，「法度law」獲得一份《拘留通知書》顯示，海口市公安局龍華分局已於今年1月18日19時將涉嫌猥褻兒童的鄭某某（即鄭冀峰）刑事拘留，羈押在海口市第一看守所。\n\n</p>\n<p>有知情人士向「法度law」透露，鄭冀峰在海南準備拍電影，選演員時猥褻兒童，被多名孩子家長報案。\n\n</p><h2>集編導演員投資人一身</h2>\n<p>相關資料顯示，鄭冀峰生於1971年，是一位導演編劇，還是金鷹電視節創立者。CCTV廣告A8論壇主席、香港HFIO資本管理公司董事長，金像影業董事長，中國文化娛樂基金合伙人。<br/>\n<br/>\n相關新聞 :<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3417798/32%E6%AD%B2%E5%89%8D%E7%A9%BA%E5%A7%90%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%9E%E8%A1%9D%E6%B5%AA%E9%81%AD%E7%8C%A5%E8%A4%BB-%E6%95%99%E7%B7%B4%E6%89%98%E8%88%89%E6%99%82%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%A1%E6%8E%A8%E7%A7%81%E8%99%95\">32歲前空姐稱三亞衝浪遭猥褻 教練托舉時多次「推私處」</a>\n</p>\n<p>同時，鄭冀峰還在多個影視與電視藝術類協會組織擔任職務。「法度Law」也曾致電上述協會，但接電工作人員以領導開會為由婉拒。\n\n</p>\n<p>鄭冀峰被公眾廣為熟知得益於參演周星馳導演的《美人魚》，出演的「鄭總」一角也是其個人銀幕首秀。\n\n</p>\n<p>該角色因為特點極為鮮明被稱「比主角還要出彩」。當時有報道指，鄭冀峰投資《美人魚》其中一個條件便是要參加演出一個角色。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2053768/即時-中國-美人魚-︱-鄭總-真身涉猥褻兒童被刑拘-曾投資周星馳作品換演出",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-20 00:11:34",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "曾志偉現身春茗撐總監製鍾澍佳 戲言對方開拍多齣劇集「搶人才」令TVB演員真空",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/65242ccdc65b57e62565d832e2732937/2025-02/page_258.jpg\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/50142252eed371efa32887c7361c0102/bd1aa046cf834779af2a57c4a39a7204-f979f516f1c98e52a58ff4aa18e4c652-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67b5fdfb00dea\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67b5fdfb00ded\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"曾志偉現身春茗支持總監製鍾澍佳 笑稱對方開拍多齣劇「搶人才」令TVB演員真空\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/ddc6a5196414170468a588452d32bf9e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250219/_2025021923274986350.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">曾志偉現身春茗支持總監製鍾澍佳 笑稱對方開拍多齣劇「搶人才」令TVB演員真空</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>曾志偉現身春茗支持「77工作室」負責人鍾澍佳，笑指對方開拍多齣劇「搶人才」令TVB演員出現真空。鍾澍佳透露今年會開多4至6部新劇，稱國內放寬演員拍攝限額，內地電視台也可播港劇，是重大突破，同時指合拍劇大有成效，在國內大受歡迎，因此產量更多需求更大。\n\n</p><h2>港劇叫好叫座</h2>\n<p>鍾澍佳表示繼佘詩曼之後，會力邀楊茜堯合作，惟未能透露內容，笑言不會安排她和老公演敵人或耍花槍，又透露《新聞女王2》於3月中開拍，爭取作為今年TVB台慶劇，故暫不開拍電影版。會否邀曾志偉拍劇？鍾澍佳笑言曾志偉只拍自己有份的賀歲片，曾志偉則笑指對方請不起自己。鍾澍佳是「77工作室」總監製，近年作品成績有目共睹︰包括《香港人在北京》（監製黃國輝）、《新聞女王》（監製關文深）、《反黑英雄》（監製方浤酌）與《黑色月光》（監製關文深）等。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091686/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"曾志偉早年與鍾澍佳合作拍賀歲片。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/592b3bd8faaaa244f58acca6d0cd57db/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-19_at_20_04_24_1.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曾志偉早年與鍾澍佳合作拍賀歲片。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091694/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"鍾澍佳、佘詩曼合作無間。 \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/488aa728a861cf0430a357cb1350b7b1/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-19_at_20_04_23_1.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鍾澍佳、佘詩曼合作無間。 \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091720/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"《新聞女王》劇照\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e45d88fc375930c22fbf1f94dc75b1ab/2025-02/w1200_10.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        《新聞女王》劇照\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091718/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"《香港人在北京》劇照\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6282a1123e5641ccc27b43a2761ab59b/2025-02/04_17.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        《香港人在北京》劇照\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091719/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"《黑色月光》劇照\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b242965f2501ee1f487f65ab6c3c99c0/2025-02/27_9.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        《黑色月光》劇照\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091687/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"曾志偉開玩笑說鍾澍佳開拍多齣劇「搶人才」令TVB演員出現真空。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5f034f5a2c564c26c435863362427e6b/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-19_at_20_31_30_1.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曾志偉開玩笑說鍾澍佳開拍多齣劇「搶人才」令TVB演員出現真空。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091688/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"曾志偉 樂易玲 鍾澍佳\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2ed5f9b1eaab8f497b589913fb473dc7/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-19_at_20_31_34_1__0.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曾志偉 樂易玲 鍾澍佳\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091689/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"春茗暨慶功宴活動有過百藝人到場支持。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/727c5dfffa4145333dca13c1a4001c49/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-19_at_20_31_43.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        春茗暨慶功宴活動有過百藝人到場支持。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091690/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"楊茜堯、曾志偉講緊咩咁開心？\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/01c1e78202e0d0717bbb3a118aafc1da/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-19_at_20_31_44_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        楊茜堯、曾志偉講緊咩咁開心？\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091691/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"曾志偉一心二用。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/90cf53aca0f2beb5893f2a6127289e6f/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-19_at_20_31_44.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曾志偉一心二用。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091692/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"楊茜堯、曾志偉老友鬼鬼。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/36bf4291af00266e4ea0c977741f42b5/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-19_at_20_31_45_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        楊茜堯、曾志偉老友鬼鬼。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
