        {
            "title": "高海寧劇透《新聞女王2》角色   對《麻雀》票房無失望 王敏奕想攞獎：遲早到自己",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/5e97d51002428c7bab858c140793c326/2025-02/ko_ling_0.jpg\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/9021d4bbeece71efbffe87c7371d0102/b0f710c223be4550be7b11930b768719-3c130f81a1dcbe0646c0fb1431191fe6-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67b5f6e8e0485\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67b5f6e8e0486\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"高海寧劇透《新聞女王2》角色   對《麻雀》票房無失望 王敏奕想攞獎：遲早到自己\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/91457cf5c5e62c6cfba8566a81e494dc/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250219/_2025021922341981081.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">高海寧劇透《新聞女王2》角色   對《麻雀》票房無失望 王敏奕想攞獎：遲早到自己</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>高海寧、王敏奕今晚(19日)到尖沙咀出席「77工作室」春茗暨慶功宴活動。將於3月底為《新聞女王2》開工，高海寧表示監製事前叫她帶獎座到場，但因全部獎座都放在父母家而未能帶出來。王敏奕被問到是否期待得獎，她笑言遲早到自己。高海寧透露已收到《新2》部分劇本，好期待。正在趕拍另一劇的王敏奕希望在《新2》開工前放幾天假休息。\n\n</p><h2>《新聞女王2》加入新血好精彩</h2>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"高海寧3月底為《新聞女王2》開工。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/db60da403c823bce834246b82d7e49dc/2025-02/0L6A0373.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        高海寧3月底為《新聞女王2》開工。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"高海寧表示已收到《新2》部分劇本。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/116ed03327398597def2561b79ca08db/2025-02/0L6A0375.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        高海寧表示已收到《新2》部分劇本。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"「77工作室」春茗暨慶功宴活動人才鼎盛。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bce2d4ce9bb8e017aaf4b48e962aabdf/2025-02/0L6A0603.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        「77工作室」春茗暨慶功宴活動人才鼎盛。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"高海寧預告在《新聞女王2》角色是從事政府新聞部。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3e79dd5470e71f46571f2a35f5b3f489/2025-02/130A8826.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        高海寧預告在《新聞女王2》角色是從事政府新聞部。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"王敏奕則說角色是個善良的人。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2b636f3f9e94f5455574fbddd9e56080/2025-02/130A8830.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        王敏奕則說角色是個善良的人。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"高海寧、王敏奕與楊茜堯合照。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/56e2180393eb56394a777b3b4119bb93/2025-02/130A8835.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        高海寧、王敏奕與楊茜堯合照。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\" 對《麻雀》香港票房僅收300萬，高海寧表示沒有失望，亦沒有壓力。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5444436c7f7ebaf17715f579c6ac1a04/2025-02/130A8841.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n         對《麻雀》香港票房僅收300萬，高海寧表示沒有失望，亦沒有壓力。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<p>高海寧、王敏奕相信續集加入新血會更精彩，高海寧預告角色從事政府新聞部，為權力而帶有目的。王敏奕透露角色是善良的人，樂見很多平台支持劇集，對市場大有好處。對於參演賀歲片《麻雀女王追男仔》香港票房僅收300萬，高海寧指戲還未上映完，票房數字亦未計海外，自己不會失望，一直無票房壓力，會出錢請公公婆婆們睇戲。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2053792/即時-娛樂-高海寧劇透-新聞女王2-角色-對-麻雀-票房無失望-王敏奕想攞獎-遲早到自己",
