            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "警破旺角毒窟 拘4男女檢多款毒品",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"警破旺角毒窟 拘4男女檢多款毒品\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/913c27149b3e3fd4c9b2589ad6bdd482/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250219/_2025021923000213335.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">警破旺角毒窟 拘4男女檢多款毒品</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>旺角警區特別職務隊人員經深入調查，今日（2月19日）突擊搜查旺角通菜街一單位，搗破一個懷疑毒窟。人員在該單位內拘捕一名58歲本地男子，涉嫌「經營毒窟」及「販運危險藥物」；兩名本地男子及一名本地女子，介乎48至63歲，則涉嫌「服食或注射危險藥物」被捕。\n\n</p>\n<p>警方在單位內檢獲4.41克懷疑可卡因、2.16克懷疑海洛英、1.5克懷疑「冰」毒及一粒懷疑藍精靈 ，市值超過7200元。所有被捕人現正被扣留調查。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091696/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"行動中警方拘捕4名男女。警方圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c5724e24e6b0cfae98eaa4883262339a/2025-02/SDS_5_MKDIST_1.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        行動中警方拘捕4名男女。警方圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2053797/即時-港聞-警破旺角毒窟-拘4男女檢多款毒品",
